com.plexobject.rx.impl

Class SubscriptionImpl<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.plexobject.rx.impl.SubscriptionImpl<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of subscription data
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Disposable, Observer<T>, SubscriptionObserver<T>, OnCompletion, Subscription

    public class SubscriptionImpl<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SubscriptionObserver<T>
    This class keeps track of user subscription including callback functions. This also allows user to unsubcribe from receiving data.
